ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/thuoc-dieu-tri-benh-ort-tren-ga\/#Benh_ORT_o_ga_la_benh_gi\" >B\u1ec7nh ORT \u1edf g\u00e0 l\u00e0 b\u1ec7nh g\u00ec?<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/thuoc-dieu-tri-benh-ort-tren-ga\/#Tai_sao_ga_lai_bi_benh_ORT\" >T\u1ea1i sao g\u00e0 l\u1ea1i b\u1ecb b\u1ec7nh ORT?<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/thuoc-dieu-tri-benh-ort-tren-ga\/#Cac_loai_thuoc_dieu_tri_benh_ORT_tren_ga\" >C\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i thu\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb b\u1ec7nh ORT tr\u00ean g\u00e0<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/thuoc-dieu-tri-benh-ort-tren-ga\/#Bien_phap_phong_tranh_de_khong_phai_dung_thuoc_dieu_tri_benh_ORT_tren_ga\" >Bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p ph\u00f2ng tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i d\u00f9ng thu\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb b\u1ec7nh ORT tr\u00ean g\u00e0<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/thuoc-dieu-tri-benh-ort-tren-ga\/#Ve_sinh_moi_truong\" >V\u1ec7 sinh m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/thuoc-dieu-tri-benh-ort-tren-ga\/#Quan_ly_che_do_dinh_duong\" >Qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/thuoc-dieu-tri-benh-ort-tren-ga\/#Phong_tranh_stress\" >Ph\u00f2ng tr\u00e1nh stress<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/thuoc-dieu-tri-benh-ort-tren-ga\/#Kiem_soat_nguon_nuoc\" >Ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t ngu\u1ed3n n\u01b0\u1edbc<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-9\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/thuoc-dieu-tri-benh-ort-tren-ga\/#Chuong_trinh_tiem_phong\" >Ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh ti\u00eam ph\u00f2ng<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-10\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/thuoc-dieu-tri-benh-ort-tren-ga\/#Ket_luan\" >K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p><strong>B\u1ec7nh ORT l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng b\u1ec7nh nhi\u1ec5m tr\u00f9ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e0n g\u00e0, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 g\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u1ea9m. S\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a b\u1ec7nh n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 g\u00e2y thi\u1ec7t h\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 kinh t\u1ebf m\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u0111e d\u1ecda s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0n. B\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, <a href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/\">Sv368<\/a> s\u1ebd gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i <a href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/thuoc-dieu-tri-benh-ort-tren-ga\/\">thu\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb b\u1ec7nh ORT tr\u00ean g\u00e0<\/a> th\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p ph\u00f2ng tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf s\u1ef1 lan truy\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a b\u1ec7nh trong \u0111\u00e0n g\u00e0.<\/strong><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Benh_ORT_o_ga_la_benh_gi\"><\/span>B\u1ec7nh ORT \u1edf g\u00e0 l\u00e0 b\u1ec7nh g\u00ec?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>B\u1ec7nh ORT l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1i b\u1ec7nh nhi\u1ec5m tr\u00f9ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn gia c\u1ea7m, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 g\u00e0. B\u1ec7nh n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y ra nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng trong \u0111\u00e0n g\u00e0, bao g\u1ed3m c\u00e1c tri\u1ec7u ch\u1ee9ng nh\u01b0 s\u01b0ng, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 h\u00f4 h\u1ea5p v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec5m tr\u00f9ng ru\u1ed9t.<\/p>\n<p>B\u1ec7nh ORT th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eb7p \u1edf gia c\u1ea7m, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c truy\u1ec1n t\u1eeb g\u00e0 nhi\u1ec5m b\u1ec7nh sang g\u00e0 kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh th\u00f4ng qua ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ho\u1eb7c qua c\u00e1c ch\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec5m tr\u00f9ng nh\u01b0 ph\u00e2n v\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc u\u1ed1ng. \u0110\u1ec3 ch\u1ea9n \u0111o\u00e1n, t\u00ecm ra thu\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb b\u1ec7nh ORT tr\u00ean g\u00e0, quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi b\u00e1c s\u0129 th\u00fa y ho\u1eb7c chuy\u00ean gia ch\u0103m s\u00f3c \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c v\u00e0 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng li\u1ec7u ph\u00e1p \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Sv368.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3115\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3115\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3115 size-full\" title=\"Thu\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb b\u1ec7nh ORT tr\u00ean g\u00e0\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/hinh-1.jpg\" alt=\"B\u1ec7nh ORT \u1edf g\u00e0 l\u00e0 b\u1ec7nh g\u00ec?\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/hinh-1.jpg?v=1709191822 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/hinh-1-300x150.jpg?v=1709191822 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/hinh-1-768x384.jpg?v=1709191822 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3115\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">B\u1ec7nh ORT \u1edf g\u00e0 l\u00e0 b\u1ec7nh g\u00ec?<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Tai_sao_ga_lai_bi_benh_ORT\"><\/span>T\u1ea1i sao g\u00e0 l\u1ea1i b\u1ecb b\u1ec7nh ORT?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh g\u00e2y ra b\u1ec7nh ORT \u1edf g\u00e0 m\u00e0 Sv368 t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u bao g\u1ed3m:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\">Nhi\u1ec5m tr\u00f9ng Salmonella: G\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb nhi\u1ec5m tr\u00f9ng b\u1edfi Salmonella qua n\u01b0\u1edbc u\u1ed1ng, th\u1ee9c \u0103n, ho\u1eb7c ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi ph\u00e2n t\u1eeb g\u00e0 nhi\u1ec5m tr\u00f9ng. Vi khu\u1ea9n n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y ra nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe, bao g\u1ed3m c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 h\u00f4 h\u1ea5p, vi\u00eam ru\u1ed9t, s\u01b0ng.<\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\">M\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0nh m\u1ea1nh: M\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ed1ng kh\u00f4ng s\u1ea1ch s\u1ebd, \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u1ea9m \u01b0\u1edbt, qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 v\u1ec7 sinh trong tr\u1ea1i g\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i cho s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 l\u00e2y lan c\u1ee7a vi khu\u1ea9n.<\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\">Stress: T\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng \u1edf g\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3m h\u1ec7 mi\u1ec5n d\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang, t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i cho vi khu\u1ea9n g\u00e2y b\u1ec7nh ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n, t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.<\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\">Ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i: Ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0103n kh\u00f4ng c\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i, k\u00e9m ch\u1ea5t dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m suy gi\u1ea3m s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe c\u1ee7a g\u00e0, l\u00e0m cho ch\u00fang tr\u1edf n\u00ean d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb b\u1ec7nh h\u01a1n.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3117\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3117\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3117 size-full\" title=\"thu\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb b\u1ec7nh ORT tr\u00ean g\u00e0\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/hinh-3.jpg\" alt=\"T\u1ea1i sao g\u00e0 l\u1ea1i b\u1ecb b\u1ec7nh ORT?\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/hinh-3.jpg?v=1709191823 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/hinh-3-300x150.jpg?v=1709191823 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/hinh-3-768x384.jpg?v=1709191823 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3117\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">T\u1ea1i sao g\u00e0 l\u1ea1i b\u1ecb b\u1ec7nh ORT?<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Cac_loai_thuoc_dieu_tri_benh_ORT_tren_ga\"><\/span>C\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i thu\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb b\u1ec7nh ORT tr\u00ean g\u00e0<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm thu\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb b\u1ec7nh ORT tr\u00ean g\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi s\u1ef1 can thi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a b\u00e1c s\u0129 th\u00fa y ho\u1eb7c chuy\u00ean gia ch\u0103m s\u00f3c \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt. Vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ecdn lo\u1ea1i thu\u1ed1c ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a b\u1ec7nh v\u00e0 m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 l\u00e2y nhi\u1ec5m trong \u0111\u00e0n g\u00e0. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 lo\u1ea1i thu\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb b\u1ec7nh ORT tr\u00ean g\u00e0 m\u00e0 Sv368 gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\">Kh\u00e1ng sinh: M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 lo\u1ea1i kh\u00e1ng sinh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t s\u1ef1 l\u00e2y nhi\u1ec5m, gi\u1ea3m t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng vi\u00eam nhi\u1ec5m. Tuy nhi\u00ean, vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kh\u00e1ng sinh c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n theo h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u1ee7a b\u00e1c s\u0129 th\u00fa y \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng kh\u00e1ng thu\u1ed1c.<\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\">Thu\u1ed1c kh\u00e1ng vi khu\u1ea9n: C\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i thu\u1ed1c kh\u00e1ng vi khu\u1ea9n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t, lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf vi khu\u1ea9n g\u00e2y b\u1ec7nh, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 c\u00e1c ch\u1ee7ng Salmonella. Tuy nhi\u00ean, vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng thu\u1ed1c n\u00e0y c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 theo d\u00f5i &amp; h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u1ee7a chuy\u00ean gia.<\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\">Dung d\u1ecbch n\u01b0\u1edbc &amp; \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb ch\u1ed1ng s\u1ed1c: Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p b\u1ec7nh ORT g\u00e2y ra s\u01b0ng v\u00e0 g\u00e2y ra t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng s\u1ed1c, dung d\u1ecbch n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cung c\u1ea5p gi\u00fap duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc &amp; \u0111i\u1ec7n gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c t\u1ebf b\u00e0o.<\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\">H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng: Cung c\u1ea5p ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0103n gi\u00e0u d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t, d\u1ec5 ti\u00eau h\u00f3a c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe c\u1ee7a g\u00e0 v\u00e0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3119\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3119\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3119 size-full\" title=\"thu\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb b\u1ec7nh ORT tr\u00ean g\u00e0\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/hinh-4.jpg\" alt=\"C\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i thu\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb b\u1ec7nh ORT tr\u00ean g\u00e0\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/hinh-4.jpg?v=1709191999 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/hinh-4-300x150.jpg?v=1709191999 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/hinh-4-768x384.jpg?v=1709191999 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3119\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">C\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i thu\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb b\u1ec7nh ORT tr\u00ean g\u00e0<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Bien_phap_phong_tranh_de_khong_phai_dung_thuoc_dieu_tri_benh_ORT_tren_ga\"><\/span>Bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p ph\u00f2ng tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i d\u00f9ng thu\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb b\u1ec7nh ORT tr\u00ean g\u00e0<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>\u0110\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n b\u1ec7nh ORT \u1edf g\u00e0 v\u00e0 tr\u00e1nh vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng thu\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p ph\u00f2ng tr\u00e1nh sau c\u1ee7a Sv368, qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd ch\u0103m s\u00f3c \u0111\u00e0n g\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. Sau \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n n\u00ean th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n:<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Ve_sinh_moi_truong\"><\/span>V\u1ec7 sinh m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\">\u0110\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o tr\u1ea1i g\u00e0 s\u1ea1ch s\u1ebd, kh\u00f4 r\u00e1o.<\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\">Th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch l\u1ed1i \u0111i v\u00e0 khu v\u1ef1c \u0103n u\u1ed1ng.<\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\">Ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 b\u00e3i b\u1ecf ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m l\u00e2y nhi\u1ec5m qua ph\u00e2n.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Quan_ly_che_do_dinh_duong\"><\/span>Qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\">Cung c\u1ea5p ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0103n c\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i, gi\u00e0u d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe c\u1ee7a g\u00e0.<\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\">\u0110\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o ngu\u1ed3n n\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ea1ch s\u1ebd, kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb nhi\u1ec5m b\u1ea9n.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Phong_tranh_stress\"><\/span>Ph\u00f2ng tr\u00e1nh stress<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\">Gi\u1ea3m thi\u1ec3u c\u00e1c y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 g\u00e2y stress nh\u01b0 thay \u0111\u1ed5i m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng, chuy\u1ec3n g\u00e0, hay nh\u1eefng bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed9t ng\u1ed9t.<\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\">Cung c\u1ea5p kh\u00f4ng gian ch\u1ee7 quan cho t\u1eebng con g\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh xung \u0111\u1ed9t trong \u0111\u00e0n.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Kiem_soat_nguon_nuoc\"><\/span>Ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t ngu\u1ed3n n\u01b0\u1edbc<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\">\u0110\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o ngu\u1ed3n n\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec5m b\u1ea9n v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a vi khu\u1ea9n.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Gi\u00e1m s\u00e1t s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u1ef3<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\">Th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n theo d\u00f5i s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3m tra tri\u1ec7u ch\u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a g\u00e0.<\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\">Ngay khi ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u b\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng, h\u00e3y li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi b\u00e1c s\u0129 th\u00fa y ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Chuong_trinh_tiem_phong\"><\/span>Ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh ti\u00eam ph\u00f2ng<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\">Tu\u00e2n th\u1ee7 ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh ti\u00eam ph\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7, \u0111\u00fang h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m nguy c\u01a1 nhi\u1ec5m tr\u00f9ng.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3116\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3116\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3116 size-full\" title=\"thu\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb b\u1ec7nh ORT tr\u00ean g\u00e0\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/hinh-2.jpg\" alt=\"Bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p ph\u00f2ng tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i d\u00f9ng thu\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb b\u1ec7nh ORT tr\u00ean g\u00e0\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/hinh-2.jpg?v=1709191823 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/hinh-2-300x150.jpg?v=1709191823 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/hinh-2-768x384.jpg?v=1709191823 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3116\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p ph\u00f2ng tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i d\u00f9ng thu\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb b\u1ec7nh ORT tr\u00ean g\u00e0<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Ket_luan\"><\/span>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Vi\u1ec7c hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c thu\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb b\u1ec7nh ORT tr\u00ean g\u00e0 l\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u00e0n g\u00e0. Tuy nhi\u00ean, vi\u1ec7c ph\u00f2ng tr\u00e1nh b\u1ec7nh b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd v\u1ec7 sinh m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng, ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng, ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t stress c\u0169ng \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng trong vi\u1ec7c ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n s\u1ef1 lan truy\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a b\u1ec7nh.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>B\u1ec7nh ORT l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng b\u1ec7nh nhi\u1ec5m tr\u00f9ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e0n g\u00e0, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 g\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u1ea9m. S\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a b\u1ec7nh n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 g\u00e2y thi\u1ec7t h\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 kinh t\u1ebf m\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u0111e d\u1ecda s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0n. B\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Sv368 s\u1ebd gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i [&#8230;]\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":3116,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[6],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-2407","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-da-ga"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2407","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2407"}